Introduction
------------
***Work Invaders***

It is my Space Invaders clone built using Pygame library. The game tells the story of a nerd who wants to get out of the clutches of the army to join a corporation.

Now:
basic sounds, random enemies, collision, score counter, game over

Soon:
main menu, Player/Enemy selection, levels



Requirements
------------
Pycharm IDE is useful.
Python==3.8.5

src/requirements.txt
pip==21.0.1
pygame==2.0.1
setuptools==54.0.0



Installation
------------
In cmd:
[Create and activate venv](https://docs.python.org/3.8/library/venv.html)
pip install requirements.txt



Usage
-----
In cmd:
cd src/
python main.py